data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled alongside Lake Kyle Park! This move-in ready 3-bed, 2.5-bath gem boasts a bright open floor plan, updated kitchen with granite counters, island, gas cooking, and recessed lighting. Enjoy the flexibility of a private dining room or office/study. Upstairs, the primary suite awaits with a walk-in closet and updated bath featuring a walk-in shower and dual vanities. Washer, dryer, and water softener included! Step outside to your private fenced backyard and patio, complemented by a detached garage for extra storage. Surrounded by nature, walking trails, and just minutes from town for convenient shopping and dining. Your perfect blend of comfort and convenience awaits! Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough
